HTTPS:

navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition() requires HTTPS

Here is my hacky way around this...

# $ pip install pyopenssl
# $ flask run --cert=adhoc

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(ssl_context='adhoc')

